Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:22.41,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 忆 之 笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拉紧钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 那边太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要随便放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 放那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 货物都在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 移动到那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都叫你别用飞的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要切断钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你能自己想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何处理你的居住权 我们尚无定论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能暂时在这里生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 就 行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Chamber 附近 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是账单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,账 单？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求贵官通过劳动补偿对机库造成的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我们赶走海贼的可是雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏机库和那是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雷德刚刚来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们为他免除了逗留期间所消耗的水电费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及将这庞然大物放在船上的装载费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只有单方受益的霸王交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我具体内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这台人形机器人太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 去搬下一箱货物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到刚刚那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 移动到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不要飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这人形机器人不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙听得懂你之外的人说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话他也会听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据军纪 在允许范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可移交命令权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板 我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快递哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在干活在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让破废铁干活 自己却在一边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大蠢材 果然还是应该把他丢进海里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可能只是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法从贵官的行动中发现意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是集中精神的一种手段罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这么热的天 亏他们还能这么好动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有纪律 他们的教官在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测 儿童的训练没有教官参与
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要如何将他们培养成社会的一员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下达下一个命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好诈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到天上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务执行出现障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请批准排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要对他们造成伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 状态怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命 中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？你在做什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道还做啊 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯 指甲 这颗星球 上 没有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的 话 就 送给 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 我们边走边聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有好礼物可以送给弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟 弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手很巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何谓「弟弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「弟弟」…就是兄弟的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己小的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旧社会中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:08:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于雌雄配偶及血缘关系而构成的社会单位的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有过这样的习俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德没有家人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低 效率 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低效率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得雷德住的地方很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔好像想问你关于宇宙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙 的 事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他对天体啦 还有能飞向宇宙的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他身体很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以无法自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身 体 虚弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的胸部有点疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河同盟中 体弱的人类将会被淘汰及处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法参加战斗的人是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用…怎么能这样 雷德你无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不 懂 你 的提 问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就去见见奥尔德姆医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔 德姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个医生 不过大家都称他为贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是加尔刚蒂亚里知识最渊博的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 艾米来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我带了客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就是雷德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说有事想问问医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我还有工作没有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 一会儿我会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面等着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听到过传言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是能理解语言的机械所发出的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项技术已经失传了 没想到能亲眼看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以 提问 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能回答得上 你就尽管问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请教如何才能回到银河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 以我的知识无法回答你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 大部分古老的智慧都已失传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是行星穿梭技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们目前所保留的关于天空的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它应该不是你所要找寻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 帮不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 也没 办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以再 问 一个 问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听你对这个舰团组织的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓见解是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰团非常没有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令体系以及军事训练也不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的行动也毫无秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解保护弱者的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星来客是这样看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所指的效率似乎相当狭义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不妨去见见贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有意义应该由你自己判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 医生也不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是雷德哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是姐姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次 见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是艾米的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也说想见见贝贝尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这就是Chamber的通信机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Chamber先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本机是用于支援驾驶员的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷 地球的语言也能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们人手不够了 你快来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 帅哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得现在气氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么气氛正好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 贝贝尔 雷德就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太急了 小心摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 姐姐总是匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥 你真的是从宇宙来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的生活是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河同盟的主要任务是与希迪亚斯进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亚斯是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威胁人类生存的异种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从银河同盟创立至今 战斗从未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这里的生活完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪消耗者唯有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 真的很艰辛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你习惯这里的生活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法理解加尔刚蒂亚的组织构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请解释低效及无意义经营的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰团不是组织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家聚在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时而吵架 时而互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这样的方式活下去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问意义何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能安心地活着不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此回答感到不解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的行动目的应该是讨伐敌人希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则人类无法获得稳定的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河同盟中 你这样的人类会立刻被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果将希迪亚斯全部都消灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河同盟会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一道命令之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果没有下一道命令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我们一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为待命不就是指一直活下去的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的人形机器人被乔给抢走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得当了次英雄 现在却不成样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道自己的行动是否有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是帮我们赶走海贼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只是在监视Chamber而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是还没适应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法判断我应该采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该采取的行动啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放弃你那军人思维怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 弃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 更加自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集雨水！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是气象现象 没有毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急事态了 用你的人形机器人来收集雨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡水可是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有帆布 把它展开来收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵官的脑波产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在意友军的战况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前状况下 贵官的思考毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得他好可怜…一个人流落到陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个帅哥没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你很担心他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你湿透了呢 会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我家把身体擦干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的骤雨很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次观测到集中降雨现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中也会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的病人也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我并不认为自己是不被需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 还有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 米？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥也是一直被别人所需要才能活到现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:20:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有对战斗有益的人才需要存活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 反向思考一下 对雷德哥哥来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有你觉得需要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐 彼此都需要对方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 我需要我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对同盟而言 无意义者没有生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这对你来说是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听姐姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这是什么 却在制作着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是笛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中完全不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛 子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它可以发出声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是 我也不 知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是想起什么悲伤的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你 把它 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是纱雅推荐的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 还是无法定位坐标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测情报不足 仍需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还需要进一步了解这个星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要 贵官早晚将与主力部队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道的
